com.xceptance.xlt.nocoding.scriptItem.action.response.extractor

Class RegexpExtractor

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.xceptance.xlt.nocoding.scriptItem.action.response.extractor.AbstractExtractor
      • com.xceptance.xlt.nocoding.scriptItem.action.response.extractor.RegexpExtractor

  • public class RegexpExtractor
extends AbstractExtractor
    Matches the pattern provided via AbstractExtractor.getExtractionExpression() and applies it to the LightWeightPage.getContent() which is created with the Context.getWebResponse(). Then, stores the match in AbstractExtractor.addResult(String).
    Author:
    ckeiner

      • execute

        public void execute(Context context)
        Compiles the pattern provided via AbstractExtractor.getExtractionExpression() and applies it to the LightWeightPage.getContent() that is created with Context.getWebResponse(). If group is specified, it only stores this matching group. Else, it stores every group.
